Bini Smaghi Refuses to Retire From ECB Early, Handelsblatt Says

-- B y   J a n a   R a n d o w
-- 
2011-05-19T07:05:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-19/bini-smaghi-refuses-to-retire-from-ecb-early-handelsblatt-says.html
European Central Bank Executive Board
member Lorenzo Bini Smaghi is refusing to leave the bank before
his term expires in 2013,  Germany ’s  Handelsblatt  reported,
citing unidentified ECB officials.  Bini Smaghi hasn’t been offered an alternative job in
exchange for making room for a French candidate after  Italy ’s
 Mario Draghi  takes over the ECB presidency from  Jean-Claude Trichet  in November, the newspaper said, without saying where it
got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jana Randow in  Frankfurt  at 
 jrandow@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at   cstirling1@bloomberg.net  